WEBVTT

00:01.710 --> 00:04.397
- Fred, stop! Stop it, Fred!
- OFJOSEPH: <i>Previously on</i> The Handmaid's Tale...

00:04.421 --> 00:06.413
<i>You let them
do that to Serena.</i>

00:06.507 --> 00:08.214
We all have
our roles to play.

00:08.300 --> 00:10.508
<i>Serena needed
to be reminded of hers.</i>

00:10.594 --> 00:11.960
Did you try
to find me?

00:12.054 --> 00:13.465
I tried so hard.

00:13.680 --> 00:14.887
Why didn't you
try harder?

00:15.724 --> 00:16.724
What did you do?

00:16.808 --> 00:20.097
I did what was best
for my child.

00:20.270 --> 00:21.602
You're getting
out of Gilead.

00:21.772 --> 00:23.559
Have a nice life!
Don't get caught!

00:24.024 --> 00:25.731
You gave her to a murderer!

00:26.610 --> 00:27.610
(SOBBING)

00:29.446 --> 00:32.109
I sent her away, Fred.
It was my choice.

00:32.323 --> 00:33.735
I drove you to desperation.

00:36.495 --> 00:37.702
It's the Handmaid.

00:38.413 --> 00:39.653
You're sweet on her,
aren't you?

00:39.790 --> 00:41.247
It's dangerous, my friend.

00:41.708 --> 00:43.324
- You're helping her escape?
- Yes.

00:43.418 --> 00:44.875
She just needs
a safe place to wait.

00:45.045 --> 00:46.045
It's your funeral.

00:46.129 --> 00:47.129
OFJOSEPH: Come on!

00:47.214 --> 00:49.456
LAWRENCE: <i>Women like you
are like children.</i>

00:49.550 --> 00:52.384
Asking for too much,
taking whatever you want.

00:52.553 --> 00:53.794
<i>Damn the consequences.</i>

00:54.137 --> 00:56.254
- Who's in the basement?
- Just Beth.

00:56.598 --> 00:58.339
<i>We saw a rat. She screamed.</i>

00:58.433 --> 00:59.514
That's a lie.

00:59.810 --> 01:02.223
I knew it was mistake
taking you in.

01:03.188 --> 01:04.349
(OFJOSEPH GRUNTS)

01:04.438 --> 01:05.725
LAWRENCE: <i>Clean it up.</i>

01:07.317 --> 01:08.728
(PANTING)

01:13.198 --> 01:15.030
- (WIND BLOWING)
- (NOOSES CREAKING)

01:17.000 --> 01:23.074
